        "timestamp": "2020-08-27 21:12:35.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nFor (1) it seems that the need is to lookup endpoints by the endpoint-id and p-interface objs by the interface-name. that can be accomplished by using the nodes api (https://docs.onap.org/en/casablanca/submodules/aai/aai-common.git/docs/AAI%20REST%20API%20Documentation/nodesQuery.html)\ni.e. \n.../nodes/p-interfaces?interface-name={interface-name} \n.../nodes/endpoints?endpoint-id={endpoint-id}\nAdding a namespace to a non top level obj will cause issues.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
